A:/> C:
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Directory Expansion Torture Test
C:/> 
C:/> # Tests that directories can grow beyond their initial 16-entry
C:/> 
C:/> # block by allocating new blocks and extending the directory
C:/> 
C:/> # inode's spans. Also tests non-contiguous directory spans by
C:/> 
C:/> # pre-fragmenting the disk.
C:/> 
C:/> #
C:/> 
C:/> # Strategy:
C:/> 
C:/> #   1. Create subdirectory BIGDIR
C:/> 
C:/> #   2. Fill its first block (16 files = 16 entries)
C:/> 
C:/> #   3. Fragment the disk to force non-contiguous allocation
C:/> 
C:/> #   4. Create more files in BIGDIR (forces directory expansion)
C:/> 
C:/> #   5. List and verify all entries are accessible
C:/> 
C:/> #   6. Read back files from both the original and expanded blocks
C:/> 
C:/> #   7. Clean up
C:/> 
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 1: Create the test subdirectory
C:/> 
C:/> MD BIGDIR
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 2: Fill the first directory block (16 entries)
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D01.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D02.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D03.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D04.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D05.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D06.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D07.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D08.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D09.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D10.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D11.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D12.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D13.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D14.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D15.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D16.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 3: Fragment the disk so the next directory block
C:/> 
C:/> # won't be contiguous with the first one.
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT GAP01.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT GAP02.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT GAP03.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT GAP04.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT GAP05.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF GAP01.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF GAP03.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF GAP05.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 4: Create more files to force directory expansion
C:/> 
C:/> # Entry 17+ must go into a new directory block
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D17.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D18.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D19.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BIGDIR/D20.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 5: Verify all entries are visible via LD
C:/> 
C:/> CD BIGDIR
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> LD
Directory Listing:
    15 D01.TXT
    15 D02.TXT
    15 D03.TXT
    15 D04.TXT
    15 D05.TXT
    15 D06.TXT
    15 D07.TXT
    15 D08.TXT
    15 D09.TXT
    15 D10.TXT
    15 D11.TXT
    15 D12.TXT
    15 D13.TXT
    15 D14.TXT
    15 D15.TXT
    15 D16.TXT
    15 D17.TXT
    15 D18.TXT
    15 D19.TXT
    15 D20.TXT
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> # Step 6: Read back files from both blocks to verify accessibility
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> # D01 is in the original block; D20 is in the expanded block
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> LF D01.TXT
scott was here
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> LF D20.TXT
scott was here
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> # Step 7: Go back to root and clean up
C:/BIGDIR> 
C:/BIGDIR> CD /
C:/> 
C:/> # Remove files in BIGDIR
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D01.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D02.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D03.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D04.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D05.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D06.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D07.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D08.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D09.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D10.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D11.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D12.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D13.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D14.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D15.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D16.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D17.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D18.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D19.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BIGDIR/D20.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RD BIGDIR
C:/> 
C:/> RF GAP02.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF GAP04.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Verify filesystem is clean
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  948736 bytes (1853 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> HALT
CPU halted
